</p>
<h3>
    Drift Fishing Methods
</h3>
<p>
    This method works best in moderate currents. Use a small weight, floating bead, and natural bait to mimic free-drifting food sources.
</p>
<h3>
    Fly Fishing for Sockeye
</h3>
<p>
